# Project

- React 19 + Vite + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS v4 + Framer Motion
- Static site for GitHub Pages user site (`base: '/'`)
- Spec-driven: implement only what is in `docs/specs/`
- Language: English

# Conventions

- Functional components only
- Static content lives in `src/data/` — never hardcode in section JSX
- One spec = one file in `src/sections/`
- UI primitives in `src/components/ui/`, layout in `src/components/layout/`
- Use `cn()` from `src/lib/cn.ts` for conditional classes

# Workflow

- Read the relevant `docs/specs/NNN-*.md` before implementing a section
- Follow `docs/DESIGN.md` for all visual decisions
- Do not add features listed as out-of-scope in `docs/SPEC.md`
